item.title: about
item.description: Every time I learned something new about Japan I grew more intrigued. When I first came to Japan in 2014 it was an interesting time in my life. In coming here I got some answers but my questions multiplied. Sure, like a lot of things I probably had an idealised view of what this place was like, but it was just fascinating from every angle. Now, I’m here.
